1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I try not to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 6]

15
00:01:07,780 --> 00:01:09,100
Ms. Chen is taking care of Master.

16
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,580
We must capture the assassin.

17
00:01:16,540 --> 00:01:17,780
The arrow is poisoned.

18
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,420
I've been planning for 10 years

19
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:22,500
for this very moment.

20
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:24,540
If you die,

21
00:01:25,220 --> 00:01:27,220
the Ye family will fall apart.

22
00:01:29,900 --> 00:01:30,660
Go check over there.

23
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:31,140
Yes!

24
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:33,940
Ten years ago,

25
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:35,980
you should have died
for my mother's death.

26
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,060
Rumeng...

27
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:46,780
Meng...

28
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:51,340
Over here!

29
00:01:51,540 --> 00:01:52,220
Stop there!

30
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:54,100
Chase him!

31
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:58,260
Let Madam know
we've caught the assassin.

32
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:12,060
What are you doing?

33
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:14,700
Why aren't you the person lying here?

34
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,260
You are behind all this.

35
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,580
Who did it?

36
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:26,420
Who hurt my grandson?

37
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:27,780
Who?

38
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:32,020
Grandmother, please don't worry.

39
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:33,940
The physician is on the way.

40
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,180
You harbinger of misfortune.

41
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,940
Since you joined the Ye family,

42
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:41,140
you've caused so much trouble.

43
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:45,940
I'm willing to go to the temple
to fast for days

44
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,500
to pray for Buhan,

45
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:49,540
only wishing for him to recover soon.

46
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,860
Get out of here!

47
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:17,500
Wait here.

48
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,700
Yes.

49
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:37,200
[Here Lies Ying, My Beloved Mother]

50
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:39,420
Mother,

51
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:42,180
I'm here to visit you.

52
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,300
Mother.

53
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:52,020
It's so cold.

54
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:57,780
I may not wait

55
00:03:57,780 --> 00:04:00,580
until the day I can clear my name.

56
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,780
Remember,

57
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:07,900
live on no matter what happens.

58
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,100
Do you remember?

59
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:13,860
Yes, Mother.

60
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:16,580
I will remember it for my life.

61
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:20,300
Now I'm a criminal.

62
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:22,060
When I'm gone,

63
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:25,460
leave this mansion.

64
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:30,500
Don't use the name Ying Hemeng anymore.

65
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:32,020
Change it to...

66
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,380
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

67
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:34,900
Chen Rumeng.

68
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:38,300
Poor girl,

69
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:41,140
you'll have to live alone in this world.

70
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:44,260
Mother, I want you with me.

71
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:47,210
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

72
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:50,740
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

73
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:52,580
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

74
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,380
I have few things with me.

75
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:57,420
Take the two incense seals,
Xiangyun and Ruyi,

76
00:04:57,940 --> 00:05:00,540
for you to remember me by.

77
00:05:02,180 --> 00:05:06,220
Make a living
with the incense-making skills

78
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:09,140
that I've taught you.

79
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:14,310
♪The dim moon reflects the bygone grief♪

80
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:17,410
♪How unforgettable it is, like a dream♪

81
00:05:17,580 --> 00:05:20,390
♪I put all the love, hate,
and grievances behind me♪

82
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:24,100
Mother!

83
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:27,420
Don't leave me.

84
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,660
Mother...!

85
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,700
If it weren't
for their harsh interrogation,

86
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:35,380
you wouldn't have fallen seriously ill

87
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:37,660
and died unjustly.

88
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,420
I will kill Ye Buhan

89
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:40,460
and bring down the Ye family.

90
00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:41,860
I'll make them all taste

91
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:43,540
the feeling of losing family.

92
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:44,650
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

93
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:49,780
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪

94
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:51,980
But he's saved me more than once.

95
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:09,340
He got in front of me again

96
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:11,540
and took that arrow for me.

97
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:15,340
I could have let him
die from the poison,

98
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:19,580
but I wasn't able to.

99
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:23,020
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

100
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,140
Mother.

101
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:26,980
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

102
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,180
What should I do?

103
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:32,540
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

104
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:35,980
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

105
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:40,980
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

106
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,540
Someone's been here.

107
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:51,780
I remember seeing him
at the Ye's Mansion when I was little.

108
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:03,300
Ying Ling?

109
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:04,620
Ying Ling!

110
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:12,740
I am Ying Hemeng.

111
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:22,340
What is meant to come cannot be avoided.

112
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:27,580
You are...

113
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:30,180
You must be Ying Ling's daughter.

114
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:35,260
You are Mr. Wen Zhong,
the incense maker

115
00:07:35,260 --> 00:07:37,660
who worked with my mother
at the Qixiang Pavilion.

116
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:39,700
Yes.

117
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:45,020
After Master Cheng died,

118
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,580
I left the Ye family.

119
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:50,860
On the day Ye Cheng died,

120
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:53,180
did my mother really go to his room?

121
00:07:59,020 --> 00:07:59,900
That night...

122
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:48,140
What... What are you doing?

123
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:12,180
Did you see who it was?

124
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:13,580
I didn't see it clearly.

125
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:16,060
I only remember

126
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,100
the person seemed tall and thin.

127
00:09:18,580 --> 00:09:20,780
They also had this pendant
hanging at their waist.

128
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,900
Seems this is related to the Bai family.

129
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,540
I need to investigate further.

130
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,140
Buhan.

131
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:49,100
Here's the porridge
I cooked for you this morning.

132
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:50,580
Try it.

133
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:02,420
I'm good.

134
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:13,820
Let me help change your dressing.

135
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,020
Buheng.

136
00:10:31,860 --> 00:10:32,900
Sorry, you'll have to suffer with me

137
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,580
at the temple for a few days.

138
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:37,620
If it weren't for you
who saved me with medicine,

139
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:39,780
I could have died on the roadside

140
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:41,820
and become a wandering spirit.

141
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:42,580
Oh, right.

142
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:45,380
Did Buheng mention
how Ye Buhan's injury is?

143
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:47,780
Mr. Ye is out of critical condition.

144
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:50,220
What's the progress
on the investigation?

145
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:51,780
Madam Ye questioned the assassin

146
00:10:51,780 --> 00:10:54,380
and found out he was hired
by Ms. Bai to kill you,

147
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:57,180
so she's forbidden us to talk about it.

148
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,660
You got Buhan hurt so badly,

149
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:16,460
yet you're sitting here
drinking your tea?

150
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:29,740
As the young lady of the Bai family,

151
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:32,100
you really shame your family

152
00:11:32,580 --> 00:11:33,980
by wearing this shabby jade pendant.

153
00:11:34,460 --> 00:11:35,260
Give it back to me.

154
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:37,820
What do you know, you rustic woman?

155
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:39,580
Go ask around.

156
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:42,020
No one except my brother and me

157
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:44,220
dares to wear
the Xiangnan White Jade in Shangjing.

158
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:45,820
Give it back to me.

159
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,100
Come and take it then.

160
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:48,740
Give it to me.

161
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:50,860
Stop it.

162
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,940
Stop it now!

163
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,620
How dare you hit me?

164
00:12:03,260 --> 00:12:04,020
I did, so what?

165
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:06,300
Ask your family to back you up then.

166
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:07,780
My brother loves me the most.

167
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:08,820
If he knows it,

168
00:12:08,980 --> 00:12:10,540
you'll be so sorry.

169
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:11,340
Who's your brother?

170
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:12,900
Let your brother show up,

171
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:13,580
liar.

172
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,540
My brother is...

173
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:27,580
But the Bai family master
is still there.

174
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:29,340
All right.

175
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:32,140
Whatever you say.

176
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:08,050
♪Familiar yet strange sights♪

177
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:10,970
♪The tale's first light♪

178
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,340
♪Growing with time's flow♪

179
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:16,880
♪Somber and mournful grief♪

180
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:20,170
♪The final act, my swan song as a bait♪

181
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:23,210
♪Has freed the heart from all desires♪

182
00:13:23,890 --> 00:13:28,210
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

183
00:13:30,530 --> 00:13:35,090
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

184
00:13:35,850 --> 00:13:40,290
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

185
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:44,450
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

186
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:47,850
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

187
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:52,890
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

188
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:57,250
♪In the face of such a bewitching gaze?♪

189
00:13:58,130 --> 00:14:03,650
♪Soft melodies caress locked windows,
reaching out to the setting sun♪

190
00:14:04,570 --> 00:14:07,090
♪Gently adorning with twilight's charm♪

191
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:10,090
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

192
00:14:10,610 --> 00:14:15,090
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪
